
open the terminal and type this 3 command lines 

first command:
./teardownFabric.sh && ./startFabric.sh && ./createPeerAdminCard.sh && cd dist && composer network install --card PeerAdmin@hlfv1 --archiveFile perishable-network.bna && composer network start --networkName perishable-network --networkVersion 0.0.1 --networkAdmin admin --networkAdminEnrollSecret adminpw --card PeerAdmin@hlfv1 --file networkadmin.card && composer card import --file networkadmin.card && composer-rest-server -c admin@perishable-network -n never -u true -w true


second command:
gnome-terminal

third command:
composer-playground

